data.description: Welcome to this charming single-story home located on a cul-de-sac street in the sought-after community of Valley Ranch, near Hwy 59, the Grand Pkwy, and a variety of amenities. Inside you'll be greeted by a flex room that could serve as an office, dining room, playroom (and more). The kitchen boasts ample counter space and a convenient breakfast bar. The open-concept design seamlessly connects the living room and kitchen, creating an ideal space for entertaining. The primary bedroom is a true retreat, featuring an en-suite bathroom with a walk-in closet, soaking tub, and a separate shower. Step outside to the backyard, where you'll find a covered patio area, a large shed, and a separate deck with a stock tank pool. This backyard is perfect for hosting summer barbecues or simply enjoying a morning cup of coffee! Don't miss the opportunity to make this delightful home yours. Schedule a showing today and experience the comfort and convenience of Valley Ranch living!
